---
import CloudsLayout from "../layouts/CloudsLayout.astro";
export const prerender = true;
---

<CloudsLayout
    title="Terms of Service | Tinyburg"
    description="Terms of Service for Tinyburg, the community trading platform for TinyTower players."
>
    <div class="relative min-h-screen px-4 py-16 sm:px-8 sm:py-20">
        <a
            href="/"
            class="bg-dark-blue/95 font-pixel shadow-pixel hover:shadow-pixel-hover fixed top-4 left-4 flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-[0.5rem] text-white backdrop-blur-sm transition-all hover:-translate-x-0.5 hover:-translate-y-0.5 sm:top-6 sm:left-6 sm:px-4 sm:py-2.5 sm:text-[0.6rem]"
            data-astro-prefetch="viewport"
        >
            <span aria-hidden="true">‚Üê</span>
            <span>Home</span>
        </a>

        <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
            <header
                class="border-gold to-sky-light/30 shadow-pixel rounded-t-2xl border-3 border-b-0 bg-linear-to-br from-white p-6 sm:p-10"
            >
                <h1 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue text-sm leading-relaxed sm:text-lg md:text-xl">
                    Terms of Service
                </h1>
                <p class="text-text-dark/60 mt-3 text-lg">Last updated: January 28, 2026</p>
            </header>

            <div
                class="border-gold bg-card-bg shadow-pixel-hover divide-y-2 divide-gray-100 rounded-b-2xl border-3 border-t-0 p-6 sm:p-10"
            >
                <section class="pb-6 sm:pb-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        1. Acceptance of Terms
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        By accessing or using Tinyburg ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service.
                        If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        You must be at least 13 years old to use the Service. By using the Service, you represent that
                        you meet this age requirement.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        2. Description of Service
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        Tinyburg is a community-driven platform that facilitates trading of in-game items, bitizens,
                        costumes, and other virtual goods between players of TinyTower, a mobile game developed by
                        NimbleBit LLC.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        All trades involve virtual goods within TinyTower. These items have no real-world monetary
                        value, and Tinyburg does not facilitate any exchange of real currency between users.
                    </p>
                    <div class="border-gold bg-gold/10 rounded-lg border-l-4 p-4">
                        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <strong class="text-dark-blue">Disclaimer:</strong> Tinyburg is an independent fan project and
                            is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or connected to NimbleBit LLC in any way. TinyTower and related
                            marks are trademarks of NimbleBit LLC.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        3. User Accounts
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        To use certain features of the Service, you must create an account using Google or Discord
                        authentication. You are responsible for:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 pl-1">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Maintaining the security of your account</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>All activities that occur under your account</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Ensuring your account information is accurate</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        4. User Conduct
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">You agree not to:</p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 pl-1">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Use the Service for any unlawful purpose</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Harass, abuse, or harm other users</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Attempt to scam or defraud other users in trades</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Impersonate other users or entities</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Interfere with the proper functioning of the Service</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Use automated systems to access the Service without permission</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        5. Trading
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        Tinyburg facilitates connections between players for trading purposes. We act solely as an
                        intermediary platform and do not participate in trades directly. Users trade at their own risk.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">Tinyburg is not responsible for:</p>
                    <ul class="mb-4 space-y-2 pl-1">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Failed, incomplete, or delayed trades</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Misrepresentation of items or user identity</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Any losses of virtual items incurred through trading</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Technical issues within TinyTower that affect trades</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                            <span class="bg-sky-dark mt-2.5 size-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span>Actions taken by NimbleBit regarding your TinyTower account</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        We encourage users to verify trade details before confirming and to report any suspicious
                        activity to our moderation team.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        6. Intellectual Property
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        The Service and its original content, features, and functionality are owned by Tinyburg and are
                        protected by applicable laws. TinyTower and related game content are the property of NimbleBit
                        LLC.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        7. Termination
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        We reserve the right to terminate or suspend your account at any time, without prior notice, for
                        conduct that we believe violates these Terms or is harmful to other users, us, or third parties.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        Upon termination, your right to use the Service will immediately cease. You may request your
                        data by contacting us before account deletion.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        8. Dispute Resolution
                    </h2>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        For disputes between users regarding trades, we encourage resolution through direct
                        communication. Our moderation team may assist but cannot enforce resolutions or recover lost
                        virtual items.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        Any disputes with Tinyburg itself shall be resolved through informal negotiation. Contact us via
                        Discord to address concerns before taking any other action.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        9. Disclaimer of Warranties
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        The Service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We do not guarantee that the
                        Service will be uninterrupted, secure, or error-free.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        10. Limitation of Liability
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        To the maximum extent permitted by law, Tinyburg shall not be liable for any indirect,
                        incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Service.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="py-6 sm:py-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        11. Changes to Terms
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        We may modify these Terms at any time. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes
                        acceptance of the modified Terms.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="pt-6 sm:pt-8">
                    <h2 class="font-pixel text-dark-blue mb-4 text-[0.55rem] leading-relaxed sm:text-[0.7rem]">
                        12. Contact
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed sm:text-xl">
                        If you have questions about these Terms, please reach out through our
                        <a
                            href="https://discord.gg/tinyburg"
                            target="_blank"
                            rel="noopener noreferrer"
                            class="text-discord decoration-discord/30 hover:decoration-discord inline-flex items-center gap-1 font-semibold underline decoration-2 underline-offset-2 transition-colors"
                        >
                            community Discord server
                            <svg class="size-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                                <path
                                    fill-rule="evenodd"
                                    d="M5.22 14.78a.75.75 0 001.06 0l7.22-7.22v5.69a.75.75 0 001.5 0v-7.5a.75.75 0 00-.75-.75h-7.5a.75.75 0 000 1.5h5.69l-7.22 7.22a.75.75 0 000 1.06z"
                                    clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</CloudsLayout>
